data.description: Welcome to this exquisite property with stunning curb appeal &charm. Nestled on a quiet interior lot within the award-winning RISD, this upgraded 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers a truly enchanting living experience with plenty of closet space & storage. Meticulously maintained landscaping invites you in with its vibrant colors and lush greenery. Step inside to discover a haven of comfort and style. The first floor boasts multiple inviting living areas, a versatile office space, well-appointed kitchen, formal dining room, and a cozy breakfast nook. The true allure of this property is the backyard oasis with a screened porch, stone bar with a piped gas grill and a convenient fridge. Your personal paradise continues with a pristine pool & a spacious deck & fire pit with a fenced backyard and side yard. Covered parking for three vehicles adds convenience, while a shed provides additional storage space for your outdoor essentials.
